c: 39
v: 3
t: "Anndee, ko Allah woodani diina laa…ìuka kan. ∆Åen non …ìe …ìeya jogitori yi…ó…ìe gaanin Makko (hara hi…ìe wi'a): \"Men alaa rewirde …ói, si wanaa tun no …ói …ìannira men ka Allah, …ìadal\". Pellet, Allah √±aawoyay hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, e kon ko …ìe woni lurrude e mun. Pellet, Allah fewnataa on won…óo fewnoowo, …óuu…óu…óo yeddugol"